    <h1 class="mt-5">API Documentation - <code>/jobs</code> Endpoint</h1>

    <h2 class="mt-4">GET /jobs</h2>
    <p>Returns a list of jobs.</p>

    <h3>Parameters</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><code>lokasjon</code> (optional): Filter jobs by location.</li>
      <li><code>order</code> (optional): Specify the order of the results.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Query Examples</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><code>https://api-test.dnul.no/jobs</code> - Retrieve all jobs.</li>
      <li><code>https://api-test.dnul.no/jobs?lokasjon=OSLO</code> - Retrieve jobs in Oslo.</li>
      <li><code>https://api-test.dnul.no/jobs?order=last</code> - Retrieve the most recent job.</li>
      <li><code>https://api-test.dnul.no/jobs?lokasjon=TRONDHEIM&order=today</code> - Retrieve jobs in Trondheim posted today.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Response</h3>
    <p>Returns a JSON array of job objects.</p>
    <pre><code>[
  {
    "id": 1,
    "company": "Example Company",
    "dato": "15/05/2023",
    "lokasjon": "Oslo",
    "description": "Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.",
    "link": "https://example.com/job1"
  },
  {
    "id": 2,
    "company": "Another Company",
    "dato": "16/05/2023",
    "lokasjon": "Trondheim",
    "description": "Sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.",
    "link": "https://example.com/job2"
  },
  ...
]</code></pre>

    <h3>Error Responses</h3>
    <p>Returns a JSON object with an error message if an error occurs.</p>
    <pre><code>{
  "error": "Internal server error"
}</code></pre>

    <h3>Example Usage</h3>
    <pre><code>GET https://api-test.dnul.no/jobs?lokasjon=Oslo</code></pre>
    <pre><code>GET https://api-test.dnul.no/jobs?order=last</code></pre>

    <h3>Notes</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>The <code>order</code> parameter supports values: <code>last</code>, <code>today</code>.</li>
      <li>The <code>lokasjon</code> parameter is case-sensitive.</li>
      <li>The response is limited to a maximum of 1 record when using the <code>order=last</code> parameter.</li>
    </ul>
